### 禁止上傳的資料夾類型
```
❌ projects/          ❌ python-main/      ❌ src/
❌ dist/              ❌ build/            ❌ assets/
❌ components/        ❌ modules/          ❌ utils/
❌ config/            ❌ lib/              ❌ scripts/
❌ docs/              ❌ examples/         ❌ tests/
